{
  "texts": [
    "Feigenbaum suggests employing the Imitation Game mechanism to assess whether a machine possesses professional-level quality.",
    "The judge's challenge in the Feigenbaum Test is to determine whether the machine shows the appropriate level of expertise in a specific domain.",
    "The judge must of course be an expert in the field.",
    "The quality of text is still an important criterion for distinguishing between humans and machines.",
    "Initial results indicated that GPT-3 could pass a variation on Turing's test (Argyle et al., 2023)."
  ]
}